[SH2:1]>>[SHO:1] set hcnt to 0
[O-:1]>>[O+0:1] set the charge to 0
[13C:1]>>[0C:1] remove the isotope 
[Pb:1]>>[#0:1] set atomic num 0, note '*' is treated as no-op
